java.io.Serializable, java.util.EventListener, prefuse.data.event.ColumnListener, prefuse.data.tuple.TupleSet, prefuse.visual.VisualTupleSet
public class GlyphTable
extends prefuse.visual.VisualTable

One of the central classes of the program. GlyphTable is a VisualTable whcih means that it holds all VisualItems that represent glyph icons. In addition it contains general data like the z axis description.
